<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Un nouvel article a été publié, n'hésitez pas à venir le consulter sur notre site internet.</p>
<h2 style="margin: 0;"><a href="{{ url('rtg_blog_newsarticle_show', { 'slug': article.slug }) }}" style="color: #428bca;">{% if article.category is not null %}{{ article.category }} : {% endif %}<span>{{ article.title }}</span></a></h2>
<div class="line-infos" style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><small style="font-size: 11px;">Par {{article.author}}</small></div>
{% if article.image is not null %}
<a href="{{ url('rtg_blog_newsarticle_show', { 'slug': article.slug }) }}" style="display: block;"><img src="{{ app.request.scheme ~'://' ~ app.request.httpHost ~ asset(article.image.webPath) }}" style="max-width: 100%;" /></a>
{% endif %}